WEBVTT

00:00:00.253 --> 00:00:03.834
"Fruit"

00:00:04.482 --> 00:00:07.369
(Special Episode)

00:00:07.999 --> 00:00:09.100
What?

00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:10.419
What are you drawing?

00:00:10.866 --> 00:00:12.666
I'll show you later.

00:00:13.666 --> 00:00:14.666
Hmph...

00:00:19.866 --> 00:00:21.162
I want to see it now.

00:00:21.781 --> 00:00:23.033
Wait a minute.

00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:29.000
Hey, you're up.

00:00:29.800 --> 00:00:30.800
Are you mad?

00:00:33.566 --> 00:00:34.202
Is it good?

00:00:34.203 --> 00:00:34.966
Yeah.

00:00:38.260 --> 00:00:39.260
Then...

00:00:41.699 --> 00:00:42.866
Let's have a competition.

00:00:43.566 --> 00:00:45.433
Okay, what are we competing?

00:00:46.100 --> 00:00:47.100
We'll...

00:00:48.246 --> 00:00:50.133
set a five-minute timer.

00:00:50.133 --> 00:00:51.466
No peeking at each other.

00:00:51.466 --> 00:00:53.033
Draw what the other person looks like.

00:00:53.932 --> 00:00:54.932
Okay.

00:00:55.666 --> 00:00:58.025
Then... your watch.

00:00:59.626 --> 00:01:01.526
Timer... starts!

00:01:34.666 --> 00:01:35.833
Time's up!

00:01:37.366 --> 00:01:38.770
I don't think so?

00:01:38.770 --> 00:01:40.666
It's up.

00:01:40.666 --> 00:01:41.900
Not yet.

00:01:42.533 --> 00:01:44.606
It's up, it's up.

00:01:44.606 --> 00:01:47.047
All right, whatever you say.

00:01:52.589 --> 00:01:55.133
Did you cheat?

00:01:55.133 --> 00:01:56.666
Of course not.

00:01:59.166 --> 00:02:00.400
What about yours?

00:02:07.219 --> 00:02:08.244
Looks good, right?

00:02:08.244 --> 00:02:09.244
Yeah.

00:02:10.533 --> 00:02:12.300
You've really improved a lot.

00:02:13.766 --> 00:02:15.366
You should be the teacher instead.

00:02:16.600 --> 00:02:19.133
Of course, these five years

00:02:19.133 --> 00:02:20.500
were not spent waiting in vain.

00:02:39.244 --> 00:02:40.244
Hmm...

00:02:41.966 --> 00:02:44.400
Then... do I win?

00:02:45.133 --> 00:02:47.700
In terms of completion, I won, no?

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:49.866
And in terms of the drawing itself?

00:02:58.066 --> 00:02:59.066
Want a bite?

00:03:12.025 --> 00:03:13.025
Miss.

00:03:14.166 --> 00:03:15.400
That's cheating!

00:03:16.939 --> 00:03:18.811
You still call me "Miss"?

00:03:18.811 --> 00:03:19.966
You're making me sound old.

00:03:22.803 --> 00:03:25.100
Otherwise, what do you want me to call you?

00:03:26.333 --> 00:03:29.144
Call you... babe?

00:03:30.132 --> 00:03:31.212
Darling?

00:03:31.773 --> 00:03:32.773
Baby?

00:03:33.121 --> 00:03:34.641
- Baby...?
- Stop messing around...

00:03:36.053 --> 00:03:38.341
Just call me by my name.

00:03:41.740 --> 00:03:42.740
Then...

00:03:45.905 --> 00:03:46.905
Ronghua?

00:03:48.721 --> 00:03:49.721
Yeah.

00:03:55.152 --> 00:03:57.733
It seems like in this competition,

00:03:57.733 --> 00:03:59.766
both of us lost completely.

00:04:11.320 --> 00:04:12.734
Still just kissing my cheek?

00:04:14.333 --> 00:04:15.500
I'm shy.

00:04:17.332 --> 00:04:18.851
Are you really that shy?

00:04:18.851 --> 00:04:20.059
Yeah...

00:04:20.059 --> 00:04:22.557
Didn't you chase after me relentlessly back then?

00:04:22.557 --> 00:04:24.002
Were you this shy?

00:04:24.002 --> 00:04:29.960
(This second, our sweet fruit.)